lyrics:
(Verse)
Happy Birthday, Nirmala, dearest friend,
With wishes warm, our love we send,
In every moment, your light shines bright,
Guiding us through both day and night.

(Verse)
In every picture, your spirit transcends,
Sharing photos of your adventures, bends,
Through valleys deep and mountains tall,
Your laughter echoes, touching all.

(Chorus)
From all your loving Modsec friends,
A chorus of joy that never ends,
With good fortune and magical moments, blend,
For you, our beautiful and caring friend.

Happy Birthday, Nirmala, dear,
May this day be filled with cheer,
With love that knows no end,
From your Modsec family, we send.
